draft}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kimotsuki Kanemori|ja|肝付兼護|12=draft|12=draft}} , military commander (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Toyohisa|ja|島津豊久|12=draft|12=draft}} , military commander (* {{ill|1570|ja|1570th year|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
