== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Battle of Sekigahara|ja|関ヶ原の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . Leads to the deaths of many people listed in [[#Deaths]] * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 18 (Gregorian {{ill|1613|ja|1613rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Hasekura Tsunenaga|ja|支倉常長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the {{ill|Keichō Embassy|ja|Keichō遣欧使節|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} from {{ill|Sendai Domain|ja|仙台藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} depart from Japan. * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1747|ja|1747th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tanuma Okitsugu|ja|田沼意次|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is appointed {{ill|Koshōgumi|ja|小姓組|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} commander. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6 (Gregorian {{ill|1853|ja|1853rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The {{ill|Ban on Large Shipbuilding|ja|大船建造の禁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is lifted, allowing large ship construction for the first time in approximately 250 years.
== Births == * {{ill|Ken’ei|ja|建炎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1130|ja|1130th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Zhu Xi|ja|朱子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , founder of {{ill|Neo-Confucianism|ja|朱子学|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1200|ja|1200th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Jōkyō|ja|貞享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1685|ja|1685th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , philosopher (+ {{ill|1744|ja|1744th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 (Gregorian {{ill|1796|ja|1796年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Date Narimune|ja|伊達斉宗|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 10th lord of {{ill|Sendai Domain|ja|仙台藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1819|ja|1819th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 (Gregorian {{ill|1825|ja|1825th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Iwakura Tomomi|ja|岩倉具視|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , politician and key figure of the {{ill|Meiji Restoration|ja|明治維新|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1883|ja|1883rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Gregorian {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Ōmori Fusakichi|ja|大森房吉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , geoscientist (+ {{ill|1923|ja|1923rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
