== Births == * {{ill|Ken’ei|ja|建炎|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 4 ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1130|ja|1130th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Zhu Xi|ja|朱子|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , founder of {{ill|Neo-Confucianism|ja|朱子学|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1200|ja|1200th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Jōkyō|ja|貞享|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 2 (Gregorian {{ill|1685|ja|1685th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 12|ja|10月12日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ishida Baigan|ja|石田梅岩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , philosopher (+ {{ill|1744|ja|1744th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8 (Gregorian {{ill|1796|ja|1796年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 15|ja|10月15日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Date Narimune|ja|伊達斉宗|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 10th lord of {{ill|Sendai Domain|ja|仙台藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1819|ja|1819th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 8 (Gregorian {{ill|1825|ja|1825th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Iwakura Tomomi|ja|岩倉具視|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , politician and key figure of the {{ill|Meiji Restoration|ja|明治維新|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1883|ja|1883rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 1 (Gregorian {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ōmori Fusakichi|ja|大森房吉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , geoscientist (+ {{ill|1923|ja|1923rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Hōen|ja|保延|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 6 (Julian {{ill|1140|ja|1140th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kakuyū|ja|覚猷|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , also known as {{ill|Toba Sōjō|ja|鳥羽Monk正覚猷|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , high-Ranking monk of the {{ill|Tendai school|ja|天台宗|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and purported creator of the {{ill|Chōjū-jinbutsu-giga|ja|鳥獣人物戯画|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kagen|ja|嘉元|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3 (Julian {{ill|1305|ja|1305th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kameyama|ja|亀山天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , 90th Emperor of Japan (* {{ill|1249|ja|1249th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 7 (Julian {{ill|1579|ja|1579th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Nobuyasu|ja|松平信康|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , eldest son of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (* {{ill|1559|ja|1559th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ōtani Yoshitsugu|ja|大谷吉継|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Hiratsuka Tamehiro|ja|平塚為広|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shima Kiyooki|ja|島清興|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Toda Katsunari|ja|戸田勝成|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kimotsuki Kanemori|ja|肝付兼護|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , military commander (* {{ill|1561|ja|1561st year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|Keichō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shimazu Toyohisa|ja|島津豊久|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , military commander (* {{ill|1570|ja|1570th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
