gorian {{ill|1853|ja|1853rd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1853|qq=}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 17|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Ban on Large Shipbuilding|ja|大船建造の禁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ban on Large Shipbuilding|qq=}} is lifted, allowing large ship construction for the first time in approximately 250 years.
