{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=九月十五|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 9월 15일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar September|qq=}} '''September 15''' is the 15th day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September (Nagatsuki)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/September (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|qq=}} .
== Events == * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Battle of Sekigahara|ja|関ヶ原の戦い|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Sekigahara|qq=}} . Leads to the deaths of many people listed in [[#Deaths]] * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 18 (Gregorian {{ill|1613|ja|1613年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1613|qq=}} {{ill|October 28|ja|10月28日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 28|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Hasekura Tsunenaga|ja|支倉常長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hasekura Tsunenaga|qq=}} and the {{ill|Keichō Embassy|ja|Keichō遣欧使節|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō Embassy|qq=}} from {{ill|Sendai Domain|ja|仙台藩|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sendai Domain|qq=}} depart from Japan. * {{ill|Enkyō|ja|Enkyō|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Enkyō|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian {{ill|1747|ja|1747年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1747|qq=}} {{ill|October 18|ja|10月18日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 18|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Tanuma Okitsugu|ja|田沼意次|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanuma Okitsugu|qq=}} is appointed {{ill|Koshōgumi|ja|小姓組|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koshōgumi|qq=}} commander. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 6 (Gregorian {{ill|1853|ja|1853年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1853|qq=}} {{ill|October 17|ja|10月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 17|qq=}} ) – The {{ill|Ban on Large Shipbuilding|ja|大船建造の禁|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ban on Large Shipbuilding|qq=}} is lifted, allowing large ship construction for the first time in approximately 250 years.
