== Deaths == * {{ill|Hōen|ja|保延|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōen|qq=}} 6 (Julian {{ill|1140|ja|1140年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1140|qq=}} {{ill|October 27|ja|10月27日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 27|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kakuyū|ja|覚猷|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kakuyū|qq=}} , also known as {{ill|Toba Sōjō|ja|鳥羽Monk正覚猷|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toba Sōjō|qq=}} , high-Ranking monk of the {{ill|Tendai school|ja|天台宗|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tendai school|qq=}} and purported creator of the {{ill|Chōjū-jinbutsu-giga|ja|鳥獣人物戯画|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōjū-jinbutsu-giga|qq=}} . * {{ill|Kagen|ja|嘉元|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kagen|qq=}} 3 (Julian {{ill|1305|ja|1305年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1305|qq=}} {{ill|October 4|ja|10月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 4|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Emperor Kameyama|ja|亀山天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Kameyama|qq=}} , 90th Emperor of Japan (* {{ill|1249|ja|1249年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1249|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 7 (Julian {{ill|1579|ja|1579年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1579|qq=}} {{ill|October 5|ja|10月5日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 5|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Matsudaira Nobuyasu|ja|松平信康|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsudaira Nobuyasu|qq=}} , eldest son of {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} (* {{ill|1559|ja|1559年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1559|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Ōtani Yoshitsugu|ja|大谷吉継|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtani Yoshitsugu|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Hiratsuka Tamehiro|ja|平塚為広|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiratsuka Tamehiro|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Shima Kiyooki|ja|島清興|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shima Kiyooki|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October 21|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Toda Katsunari|ja|戸田勝成|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toda Katsunari|qq=}} , military commander. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 5 (Gregorian {{ill|1600|ja|1600年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1600|qq=}} {{ill|October 21|ja|10月21日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oc